(58913, 168948, 0, 1, 'Baby Come Back', '編曲:裴崇伯', '2013-01-12 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 2, 4, '我陷入回憶漩渦 妄想和你重新來過\r\n但你的眼裡已經不再是我\r\n怪我老自負過頭 那些年也瘋過愛過\r\n韓風來襲過後 我終於才懂\r\n\r\nHow to live my life~ \r\nWHO ? WHERE ? WHEN ? WHY ?\r\nCan stay on my mind ?\r\n\r\n當鏡頭已經轉了頭  tuned out \r\nHo baby please come back come back\r\nI will show you 我認錯 我願改過\r\nHo baby please come back come back\r\n\r\nstay with me\r\nhow much i need you\r\nMY Broken Hearted Baby Come Back\r\n', '', 225, '', '郭重佑', '楊哲彥,江淑薇', '郭重佑', '本勵門', '', 0, 1, 0, '2013-01-12 12:37:34', '2015-03-12 13:58:27', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
